Class ComplexMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • math.ComplexMatrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ComplexMatrix
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Contains a complex matrix as a two-dimensional array of complex numbers, and includes methods for basic complex matrix operations.
    Author:
    ydna
